{"tid":765944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"坐地鐵俾人屌唔讓座你地會點答？","createTime":"2018-08-03T07:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T10:47:59.000Z","uid":17488,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"428d25711d837628d5f52d36228b962fb795904e","tid":765944,"uid":17488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"剛剛發生我身上面<br />\n帶住耳塞聽歌<br />\n無喇喇一個女人指住我地一排幾個後生<br />\n：如果我係你老豆老母真係唔想認你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有老人家唔讓座 仲要有講有笑<br />\n駁左幾句已經覺得好憨鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要加句香港淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港淪陷佢地啲上一代無份造成咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾時香港連位都唔俾坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我以為唔好打關愛座主意已經無死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地會點答啲死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25ad3f296f6d1d7c1ce120a4546e0984edbe5e2","tid":765944,"uid":36857,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T07:45:49.000Z","msg":"直接屌柒佢老母個冚家鏟咪得囉，講咁多把撚咩"},{"pid":"83c6e6a4c9da3fc98bff127fedad33c40d822188","tid":765944,"uid":838,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T07:46:14.000Z","msg":"有位坐係我本事 點解要讓<br />\n屌你老母🖕🏻"},{"pid":"83d672c3422c197d9ecf0647b152e90092991b94","tid":765944,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc